“audio  recording”  means  any  material  on  which  is  recorded  a 
recording of a human voice or of instrumental music or other sounds 
and includes phonograph records, tapes and laser discs;

(b) all  written  or  printed  matter  and  everything  whether  of  a 
nature  familiar  to  written  or  printed  matter  or  not 
containing any visible representation;

(a)  prohibit  the  importation  of  any  or  all  publications 
whether  before  or  after  the  date  of  the  order,  subject  to 
such conditions as may be prescribed therein;
